---
---

<section class="section-pad" id="explore" data-screen-label="Things to do">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal" style="max-width:760px">
      <p class="eyebrow">Explore like a local</p>
      <h2>Craft brews, local eatery favorites, and the best ice cream you've ever had! This is our playground. Let us show you around.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="todo reveal">
      <a class="todo__card" href="#results">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502933691298-84fc14542831?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=80" alt="Surfing" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="todo__body">
          <div class="todo__kicker">Surf &amp; sand</div>
          <h3>Catch a morning set</h3>
          <p>Tourmaline and Cardiff Reef are forgiving for beginners; Black's Beach rewards the brave.</p>
          <span class="todo__tip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6 4.6 2.3 7.4-6.3-4.6-6.3 4.6L8 14 2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>Local tip: dawn patrol beats the crowds</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="todo__card" href="#results">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565299624946-b28f40a0ae38?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=80" alt="Tacos" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="todo__body">
          <div class="todo__kicker">Food &amp; drink</div>
          <h3>Eat your way down the coast</h3>
          <p>From fish tacos in OB to Little Italy's pasta and the breweries of North Park.</p>
          <span class="todo__tip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6 4.6 2.3 7.4-6.3-4.6-6.3 4.6L8 14 2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>Local tip: go early, lines are real</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="todo__card" href="#results">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534430480872-3498386e7856?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=80" alt="Family fun" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="todo__body">
          <div class="todo__kicker">Family adventures</div>
          <h3>Beyond the big parks</h3>
          <p>Balboa Park museums, the Birch Aquarium, and tide pools the kids won't forget.</p>
          <span class="todo__tip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6 4.6 2.3 7.4-6.3-4.6-6.3 4.6L8 14 2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>Local tip: free museum Tuesdays</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:36px"><a href="/blog" class="btn">Discover San Diego</a></div>
  </div>
</section>
